1. High energy lasers.(Laser cannons, or molecular disruptors)<br>
Types:<br>
a. Electricly pumped co2 lasers- fires high energy uv/ir<br>
laser beam at you .<br>
b. free electron lasers-fires uv/xray frequancy high energy<br>
laser beam at you<br>
c. chemical lasers-fires uv or Ir frequancy laser beam created by high energy chemical laser at you<br>
2. Neutral particle beam weapons.(Ion cannons, or atomic disrupters )<br>
types:<br>
A. proton cat-ion  cannon- fires high energy neutral proton beam at you created by ac/av cyclotron, synchroton, or linear particle acclerator at you <br>
b. proton An-ion cannon - fires Neutral high energy<br>
proton beam created by a traveling wave compact<br>
negative ion particle accelerator at you .<br>
3. kinetic kill, high  explosive and nuclear warhead, or evene antimatter warhead  tipped missiles.I call them space torpedos.Run into traget or blow it up<br>
4.Electron particle beam weapons (giant ultra high energy tasers, or electric stun guns ). I call them Electron cannons.<br>
Zaps you literally with man made lightening<br>
5. Neutral anti-proton particle  beam weapons<br>
two types<br>
a. Antiproton ion  cannon - fires a high energy beam of <br>
antihydrogen atoms at you .<br>
b.anti-proton plasma cannon -fires a blop of antimatter<br>
plasma at you  through a magnetic nozzle<br>
 (they could  be called Phasers if we want)<br>
Anybody want to discuss these technologies here?<br>
Tim<br>
6. Also conventional terrestial type artillery , and machine guns could be used effectively as kkv projectiles,<br>
or explosive shells on you in space.<br>
* Even the cannons of 16th century  Tudor England or the 16 th century spanish naval fleet could be used as effective kinetic kill projectile weapons in space even in leo<br>
7. Armed Battle Stars, armed space stations, armed sattilites  and armed space battle cruisers.<br>
